      "releaseNotes": "Lock in exclusive April Monthly Perks! Choose between earning 100 Bonus Points When You Buy 7-Select Water, Energy, and Isotonic drink or earning 2X points on a Hot Dog, Grill Item, or Pizza Slice.\n\nFor a better delivery experience, the order tracker screen is enhanced with more transparent, real‑time updates, making it easier for you to track your orders from start to finish.",
      "version": "4.2603.0",
