      "currency": "USD",
      "description": "Join. Earn. Get Rewarded.\n \nSHOP & EARN REWARDS  \nGet rewards points on your everyday purchases when you scan your app barcode*, then browse our rewards menu and use points to get free food and drinks. Earn faster with bonus points offers and point streaks on select snacks, drinks, and products. Don’t forget to take advantage of our punch cards to unlock additional free rewards!\n\nFIND DEALS \nGet exclusive offers and money-saving deals on your favorite products like pizza, coffee, ice cream, donuts, snacks, energy drinks and bottled water for 7Rewards members. \n\nORDER DELIVERY \nGet food, alcohol, candy, snacks, drinks, ice cream, coffee, groceries, health needs, household essentials, and more delivered anywhere you are in about 30 minutes. Super-Fast Delivery. Get your order delivered to your door 24/7. We deliver over 5000+ items including Slurpee® and Big Gulp®, coffee, pizza and sandwiches, and even beer, wine, and liquor (where available, 21 years or older of course) across major metro areas.\n\nNEW! LOCAL RESTAURANT DELIVERY\nEnjoy meals from your favorite local restaurants delivered straight to your door. Available in select locations only.\n\nFUEL SAVINGS & PRICE LOCK\nFind our 7-Eleven branded gas stations and fill up on gas for less. On your first 7 trips, you'll save 11¢/gal. After that, you'll receive everyday member savings of at least 5¢/gal (varies by state). Plan your next gas station visit today with Price Lock. Price Lock secures the gas price for 4 days in a participating gas station by finding the lowest fuel prices around you and holds the price for you with Price Lock. Unlock and Re-Lock anytime and know you will always get the best price even if your locked price is higher.\n\n7-ELEVEN WALLET \nIt's easy to pay with your phone. The 7-Eleven Wallet makes checking out contactless and easy. Get started when you load your Wallet with cash, credit, debit, 7-Eleven gift cards or Apple Pay®.\n   \nMOBILE CHECKOUT - (AVAILABLE AT SELECT 7-ELEVEN LOCATIONS)  \nWith our contactless checkout, you can shop and check out with your phone. It’s as easy as scan, pay, and go. Scan the items as you shop and skip the line when you are ready to checkout. What’s more, Mobile checkout users get discounts, exclusive deals, special rewards, and rewards points on every transaction.\n\nNOW AVAILABLE AT STRIPES STORES  \nStart saving big and earning rewards points on everything you buy at Stripes stores. Redeem points for free food and drinks. Get tacos and family meals from Laredo Taco Company, beer, and groceries to go with curbside pickup at select stores.\n\n*Points exclude services, fuel and age-restricted items including tobacco, lottery and alcohol",
